      "markText": "多年以后，面对行刑队，奥雷里亚诺·布恩迪亚上校将会回想起父亲带他去见识冰块的那个遥远的下午。",
      "totalCount": 65632,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=369&rangeEnd=415"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_44_11774-11872",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "11774-11872",
      "markText": "这座镜子之城——或蜃景之城——将在奥雷里亚诺·巴比伦全部译出羊皮卷之时被飓风抹去，从世人记忆中根除，羊皮卷上所载一切自永远至永远不会再重复，因为注定经受百年孤独的家族不会有第二次机会在大地上出现。",
      "totalCount": 44213,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=11774&rangeEnd=11872"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_41_12841-12883",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "12841-12883",
      "markText": "在最后一刻的慌乱中，悲伤的醉汉们抬棺材出家门时弄混了，把两人各自下葬在对方的坟墓里。",
      "totalCount": 37410,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=12841&rangeEnd=12883"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_32_12072-12131",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "12072-12131",
      "markText": "你那么憎恨军人，跟他们斗了那么久，琢磨了他们那么久，最终却变得和他们一样。人世间没有任何理想值得以这样的沉沦作为代价。",
      "totalCount": 32793,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=12072&rangeEnd=12131"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_44_2700-2752",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "2700-2752",
      "markText": "不论在什么地方都要记住，过去都是假的，回忆没有归路，春天总是一去不返，最疯狂执著的爱情也终究是过眼云烟。",
      "totalCount": 27870,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=2700&rangeEnd=2752"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_32_4032-4068",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "4032-4068",
      "markText": "“只要上帝还让我活着，”她时常这样说，“这个净出疯子的家里就缺不了钱。”",
      "totalCount": 22256,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=4032&rangeEnd=4068"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_26_11897-11938",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "11897-11938",
      "markText": "乌尔苏拉没有追上吉卜赛人，却找到了丈夫在失败的远征中没能发现的通向伟大发明的道路。",
      "totalCount": 19815,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=11897&rangeEnd=11938"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_35_11081-11125",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "11081-11125",
      "markText": "她辛苦多年忍受折磨好不容易赢得的孤独特权，绝不肯用来换取一个被虚假迷人的怜悯打扰的晚年。",
      "totalCount": 19348,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=11081&rangeEnd=11125"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_25_1319-1368",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "1319-1368",
      "markText": "“科学消除了距离，”梅尔基亚德斯说，“用不了多久，人们不出家门就能看到世界上任何地方发生的事情。”",
      "totalCount": 18192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=1319&rangeEnd=1368"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_30_4070-4100",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "4070-4100",
      "markText": "“别天真了，克雷斯皮，”她微笑着，“我死也不会和你结婚的。”",
      "totalCount": 17925,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=4070&rangeEnd=4100"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_27_7710-7731",
      "chapterUid": 27,
      "range": "7710-7731",
      "markText": "他的确一度死去，但难以忍受孤独又重返人世。",
      "totalCount": 17838,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=27&rangeStart=7710&rangeEnd=7731"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_30_10901-10994",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "10901-10994",
      "markText": "“告诉我女人，”他声音非常平静，“给女儿起名乌尔苏拉。”他顿了一下，重复道，“乌尔苏拉，跟她祖母一样。再告诉她如果生了男孩，就叫他何塞·阿尔卡蒂奥，但不是随他伯父的名字，而是随他祖父。”",
      "totalCount": 17391,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=10901&rangeEnd=10994"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_33_2954-3009",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "2954-3009",
      "markText": "奥雷里亚诺·布恩迪亚上校没有显出丝毫不快，但在私人卫队将那位寡妇的家舍夷为平地化为灰烬之后，他的心才恢复平静。",
      "totalCount": 17104,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=2954&rangeEnd=3009"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_33_1954-1981",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "1954-1981",
      "markText": "“奥雷里亚诺，”他悲伤地敲下发报键，“马孔多在下雨。”",
      "totalCount": 17052,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=1954&rangeEnd=1981"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_30_4637-4686",
      "chapterUid": 30,
      "range": "4637-4686",
      "markText": "在这纷乱的合奏中，皮埃特罗·克雷斯皮伏在店后的写字台上，双腕用剃刀割破，双手浸没在一盆安息香水里。",
      "totalCount": 16960,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=30&rangeStart=4637&rangeEnd=4686"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_25_8768-8804",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "8768-8804",
      "markText": "“我们还没有死人，”他说，“只要没有死人埋在地下，你就不属于这个地方。”",
      "totalCount": 16524,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=8768&rangeEnd=8804"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_41_6209-6263",
      "chapterUid": 41,
      "range": "6209-6263",
      "markText": "她死在圣星期四一早。人们最后一次帮她数算年龄是在香蕉公司时期，当时得出的结果在一百一十五到一百二十二岁之间。",
      "totalCount": 15804,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=41&rangeStart=6209&rangeEnd=6263"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_25_5891-5914",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "5891-5914",
      "markText": "它的确是一处乐土，没人超过三十岁，也没人死去。",
      "totalCount": 15360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=5891&rangeEnd=5914"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_31_11812-11859",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "11812-11859",
      "markText": "“我谁也不嫁，”她告诉他，“尤其不嫁给你。你太爱奥雷里亚诺才想跟我结婚，因为你没法跟他结婚。”",
      "totalCount": 15093,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=11812&rangeEnd=11859"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "935536_25_3263-3347",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "3263-3347",
      "markText": "他在波斯得过蜀黍红斑病，在马来群岛患上坏血病，在亚历山大生过麻风病，在日本染上脚气病，在马达加斯加患过腺鼠疫，在西西里碰上地震，在麦哲伦海峡遭遇重大海难，却都大难不死。",
      "totalCount": 15066,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=935536&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=3263&rangeEnd=3347"
    }
  ],
